title: Auf Wiedersehen Pet Series 1 Episode 1
description:
1. If I were a carpenter.
Originally Broadcast 11-11-1983

Synopsis - In a desperate effort to find work, three Georide bricklayers, Dennis, Neville and Oz, journey to Germany hoping for tax free wages, beautiful frauleins and cheap beer.  What they find instead is a wooden hut, and to make matters worse, Neville must masquearade as a carpenter.

Enjoy,Please Seed.
